# 载入图片并显示
# Load package
import cv2
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np


# -------------Type your code here-------------
# TODO: load image "winnie.jpeg", place it in variable "image"
image = cv2.imread("winnie.jpeg")

# --------------------------------

(b, g, r) = image[0, 0]
print("Pixel at (0, 0) - Red: {}, Green: {}, Blue: {}".format(r,g, b))
image[0, 0] = (0, 0, 255)
(b, g, r) = image[0, 0]
print("Pixel at (0, 0) - Red: {}, Green: {}, Blue: {}".format(r,g, b))

#--------code for showing image------------

# transfer BGR to RGB 
# (Because plt show image in RGB, but opencv load image in BGR)
image = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)

# set image to show
plt.imshow(image)
# set title
plt.title("Winnie the Pooh")
# show image
plt.show()

In [32]:
# 为了以后方便显示，把显示方法放入show_image方法中
# title 图片标题，image 存储图片的数组
def show_image(title,image):
    image = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
    # set image to show
    plt.imshow(image)
    # set title
    plt.title(title)
    # show image
    plt.show()

# show Origin image    
image = cv2.imread("./winnie.jpeg")
show_image("Origin",image)

  • 考察内容：
    • Lines
    • Rectangle
    • Circles

# 创建白色画布，在里面画图形：实心矩形，空心矩形，实心圆形，空心圆形，直线

# -------Type in your code below-------------
# 创建白色画布
canvas = np.zeros((300,300,3),dtype = "uint8")
black = (255,255,255)
# 画线
cv2.line(canvas,(0,0),(300,300),black)
# 画矩形
cv2.rectangle(canvas, (15, 15),(30,40), black)
cv2.rectangle(canvas, (30, 40),(50,70), black,-1)
# 画圆形
cv2.circle(canvas, (150, 150), 33, black)
cv2.circle(canvas, (200, 200), 33, black,-1)
# ------------show canvas--------------------
show_image("Canvas",canvas)

题目二¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Translation
    • Rotation
    • Resizing
    • Flipping

In [45]:
image = cv2.imread("./winnie.jpeg")
show_image("Origin",image)
# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# 1.向右50 pixel，向上90 pixel
M = np.float32([[1, 0, -90], [0, 1, 50]])
shifted = cv2.warpAffine(image, M, (image.shape[1], image.shape
[0]))
show_image("Shifted Up and Right",shifted)

# 2.上一次修改后的图形绕中心顺时针旋转45度
(h,w) = image.shape[:2]
center = (w //2, h // 2)

M = cv2.getRotationMatrix2D(center, -45, 1.0)
rotated =  cv2.warpAffine(image, M, (w, h))
show_image("Rotated by 45 Degrees",rotated)

# 3.上一次修改后的图形按照宽度（width）变成200 pixel进行等比例缩小(使用)
r = 200.0/ image.shape[1]
dim = (200, int(image.shape[0] * r))
resized = cv2.resize(image, dim, interpolation = cv2.INTER_AREA)
show_image("Resize Width",resized)

# 4.上一次修改后的图形水平对称图片(使用)
flipped = cv2.flip(image, 1)
show_image("Flipped Horizontally",flipped)

# 5.在上一次修改后的图形中把小熊维尼的头像剪切出来
cropped = image[50:50 , 100:110]
show_image("Winnie's Face",cropped)

题目三¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Image arithmetic
    • Bitwise Operation
In [34]:
show_image("Origin",image)

# -------------Type your code below-------------------

# 原图片所有的像素点数值加20
M = np.ones(image.shape, dtype = "uint8") * 20
addImage = cv2.add(image, M)
show_image("Add 20 intensity",addImage)

# 原图片所有的像素点数值减20
subImage = cv2.subtract(image,M)
show_image("Subtract 20 intensity",subImage)

# addImage 和 subImage 进行亦或处理
bitwiseXor = cv2.bitwise_xor(addImage, subImage)
show_image("bitwise and",bitwiseXor)

题目四¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Masking
In [39]:
# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# 1.create mask's canvas
mask = np.zeros(image.shape[:2], dtype = "uint8")
(cX,cY) = (image.shape[1] // 2, image.shape[0] // 2)
cv2.rectangle(mask, (cX-95, cY-95), (cX+95, cY+95), 255, -1)
#----------show mask(Don't Change any of these)--------
plt.title("mask")
plt.imshow(mask,cmap = plt.cm.gray)
plt.show()
#-----------------------------------------------------

# 2.Place mask
masked = cv2.bitwise_and(image, image, mask = mask)
show_image("Mask Applied to Image",masked)

题目五¶

  • 考察内容：
    • Splitting channels
    • Merging channels
In [40]:
# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# Split the image
# 将图片拆分成B、G、R，用彩色图分别显示
(B, G, R) = cv2.split(image)
zeros = np.zeros(image.shape[:2], dtype = "uint8")
show_image("Blue", cv2.merge([B, zeros, zeros]))
show_image("Green", cv2.merge([zeros, G, zeros]))
show_image("Red", cv2.merge([zeros, zeros, R]))

# -------------Type your code below-------------------
# 显示三种类型的图：gray，hsv，lab
gray = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2GRAY)
hsv = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2HSV)
lab = cv2.cvtColor(image, cv2.COLOR_BGR2LAB)

# -----------------show image------------------------
plt.imshow(gray,cmap = plt.cm.gray)
plt.show()
plt.imshow(hsv)
plt.show()
plt.imshow(lab)
plt.show()
